write code in golang
build a library that can be linked in to a C++ application
this library should allow a C++ application to connect to a database
create a database pool based on a mssql server connection string
allow creating a pool and giving the pool a name and a connection string
c++ application should be able to query the database using the pool name
sql commands could be select or insert or update or delete and may take parameters
the c++ application should be able to execute the sql command and return the results
the c++ application should be able to close the connection to the database and tear down the pool
the pool should keep a minimum number of connections open
the pool should have a maximum number of connections
the pool should be a mssql driver based pool
the pool should be able to handle connection errors and retries
the pool should be able to handle connection timeouts
